#: ../../docs/classes/class_tilemap.rst:322
msgid ""
"If ``true``, the textures will be centered in the middle of each tile. "
"This is useful for certain isometric or top-down modes when textures are "
"made larger or smaller than the tiles (e.g. to avoid flickering on tile "
"edges). The offset is still applied, but from the center of the tile. If "
"used, :ref:`compatibility_mode "
"<class_TileMap_property_compatibility_mode>` is ignored."
msgstr ""
"如果为 "
"``true``，则纹理将居中于每个图块的中间。当纹理大于或小于图块时，这对于某些等距或自上而下的模式很有用（例如，避免在图块边缘闪烁）。偏移仍然适用，但从图块的中心应用。如果使用，则忽略"
" :ref:`compatibility_mode <class_TileMap_property_compatibility_mode>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_tilemap.rst:324
msgid ""
"If ``false``, the texture position start in the top-left corner unless "
":ref:`compatibility_mode <class_TileMap_property_compatibility_mode>` is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``false``，则除非启用了 :ref:`compatibility_mode "
"<class_TileMap_property_compatibility_mode>`，否则纹理位置将从左上角开始。"

