#: ../../docs/classes/class_tilemap.rst:436
msgid ""
"If ``true``, the compatibility with the tilemaps made in Godot 3.1 or "
"earlier is maintained (textures move when the tile origin changes and "
"rotate if the texture size is not homogeneous). This mode presents "
"problems when doing ``flip_h``, ``flip_v`` and ``transpose`` tile "
"operations on non-homogeneous isometric tiles (e.g. 2:1), in which the "
"texture could not coincide with the collision, thus it is not recommended"
" for isometric or non-square tiles."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``true``，则将保持与Godot "
"3.1或更早版本中，制作的图块地图的兼容性（当图块原点发生更改时纹理将移动，如果纹理尺寸不均匀则纹理将旋转）。在非均匀等距图块（例如2:1）上执行"
" ``flip_h``、``flip_v`` 和 ``转置（transpose）`` "
"图块操作时，此模式会出现问题，图块中纹理可能与碰撞不一致，因此，不建议将其用于等轴测图或非正方形图块。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_tilemap.rst:438
msgid ""
"If ``false``, the textures do not move when doing ``flip_h``, ``flip_v`` "
"operations if no offset is used, nor when changing the tile origin."
msgstr "如果为 ``false``，则在执行 ``flip_h``、``flip_v`` 操作（如果不使用偏移量），或更改图块原点时，纹理不会移动。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_tilemap.rst:440
msgid ""
"The compatibility mode doesn't work with the :ref:`centered_textures "
"<class_TileMap_property_centered_textures>` option, because displacing "
"textures with the :ref:`cell_tile_origin "
"<class_TileMap_property_cell_tile_origin>` option or in irregular tiles "
"is not relevant when centering those textures."
msgstr ""
"兼容性模式不适用于 :ref:`centered_textures "
"<class_TileMap_property_centered_textures>` 选项，因为当居中这些纹理时，显示纹理与，使用 "
":ref:`cell_tile_origin <class_TileMap_property_cell_tile_origin>` "
"选项，或是否在不规则图块中无关。"

